                    <li>Visit <a href="https://parivahan.gov.in/" class="for-link">parivahan.gov.in</a></li>
                    <li>Fill "Transfer of Ownership" form</li>
                    <li>Upload documents & pay fees (₹150–₹300)</li>
                    <li>Download receipt and await new RC</li>
                </ul>

